Package: mapmixture
Title: Spatial Visualisation of Admixture on a Projected Map
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tom", "Jenkins", , "tom.l.jenkins@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: mapmixture is an R package and shiny app that enables users to 
    visualise admixture as pie charts on a projected map. It also allows users 
    to visualise admixture as traditional structure barplots or facet barplots.
License: GPL (>= 3)
